<div class="sp-containment">
<div class="sp-containment-image">
<div class="scp-image-block block-right"><img src="http://scptestwiki.wikidot.com/local--files/members:scp-wt-woedcode-5/location-scp-0000.png" alt="location-scp-0000.png" class="image" />
